issue.body:
Error while importing sale_saleConfig.csv
com.axelor.data.ImportException: Constraint violation error:

- [company] - ne doit pas être nul

there are important changes between version 7.1.6 and 7.2.0 on file "sale_saleConfig.csv".
The issue may come from there.

FYI i tried to install version 7.2.0 from scratch, while i faced this issue.

[sale_saleConfig_after_(version_7.2.0).csv](https://github.com/axelor/axelor-open-suite/files/13178369/sale_saleConfig_after_.version_7.2.0.csv)
[sale_saleConfig_before_(version_7.1.6).csv](https://github.com/axelor/axelor-open-suite/files/13178370/sale_saleConfig_before_.version_7.1.6.csv)
